back\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 01, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104beo1719857754417.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/beo1719857754417.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/beo1719857754417.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dny1665702599174\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $totdbocc\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dny1665702599174___totdbocc_292469\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the number of occurrences of the entity that have been retrieved from a database.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dny1665702599174__topic_d90191e1_d90192e1_d90193e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dny1665702599174__p_d90194e1_d90195e1_d90196e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dny1665702599174__topic_d60032e1_d60033e1_d60034e1_d60035e1_d60036e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d464825e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dny1665702599174__topic_d60037e1_d60038e1_d60039e1_d60040e1_d60041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d464825e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9812e1_d9813e1_d9814e1__entry__2\">\n Total number of occurrences of the specified entity currently fetched from the database.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1102\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dny1665702599174__table_d9815e1_d9816e1_d9817e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dny1665702599174__topic_d60042e1_d60043e1_d60044e1_d60045e1_d60046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d464825e238\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dny1665702599174__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dny1665702599174__topic_d60047e1_d60048e1_d60049e1_d60050e1_d60051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d464825e248\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dny1665702599174__p_d90212e1_d90213e1_d90214e1\">The following events affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dny1665702599174__li_d35756e1_d35757e1_d35758e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span> adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dny1665702599174__li_d35759e1_d35760e1_d35761e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span> reduces <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span> if a database occurrence is discarded\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dny1665702599174__li_d35762e1_d35763e1_d35764e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span> to 0\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dny1665702599174__p_d90215e1_d90216e1_d90217e1\">The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totdbocc</span> equals <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span> only when all the occurrences in the hitlist have been read.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dny1665702599174__section_ah1_ts4_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d464825e299\">Example: Calculating Entered but Unstored Occurrences </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, the number of occurrences in the component is\n            compared with the number of occurrences in the database. If there are more occurrences\n            in the component, the ProcScript assumes that occurrences have been added to the\n            component structure. The number of database occurrences is subtracted from the number of\n            component occurrences, and the result is inserted into a message sent to the user:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dny1665702599174__pre_uxb_5s4_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail\nif ($totocc &gt; $totdbocc)\n $1 = ($totocc - $totdbocc)\n message \"%%$1 customer(s)%%% have been added\"\nendif\nend; detail</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmg1665702599090.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curhits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgk1665702598390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmp1665702598941.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totocc</a><p>Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$totdbocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 01, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $totdbocc Return the number of occurrences of the entity that have been retrieved from a database. $totdbocc { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $totdbocc Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >0 Total number of occurrences of the specified entity currently fetched from the database. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $totdbocc Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The following events affect the value of $totdbocc : read adds 1 to $totdbocc discard reduces $totdbocc if a database occurrence is discarded clear sets $totdbocc to 0 The value of $totdbocc equals $hits only when all the occurrences in the hitlist have been read. Example: Calculating Entered but Unstored Occurrences In the following example, the number of occurrences in the component is compared with the number of occurrences in the database. If there are more occurrences in the component, the ProcScript assumes that occurrences have been added to the component structure. The number of database occurrences is subtracted from the number of component occurrences, and the result is inserted into a message sent to the user: trigger detail if ($totocc > $totdbocc) $1 = ($totocc - $totdbocc) message \"%%$1 customer(s)%%% have been added\" endif end; detail Copy Related Links $curhits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $hits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. $totocc Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}